DESCRIPTION:Spray City Walls Graffiti Battle \nEvery 3rd Friday | 8 – 11 PM
	 | Free Entry!\n\nGet ready to immerse yourself in a world of creativity\,
	 colors\, and culture as we celebrate the beauty of art at Spray City Wall
	s Graffiti Battle!\n\nHighlights of the event:• Live mural painting select
	 artists• Delicious craft beers and beverages• Live music and entertainmen
	t• Artist market & vendors• Community engagement and more!\n\nDon’t miss t
	he chance to be a part of this vibrant celebration of art and expression. 
	Whether you’re an art enthusiast\, a foodie\, or just looking for a fun da
	y out\, this event has something for everyone.Save the date and spread the
	 word! We can’t wait to share this unforgettable experience with you.\n\nh
